                If you have any questions, feel free to contact us at <%= mail_to "contact@ggc.ch" %>.<br/>
                Your GGC team.
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="text-align:center; max-width:800px; margin-bottom:1em; background-color:#e3e3e3;">
